PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/>
PREFIX : <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/>
PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>

    PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
    PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
    PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

SELECT ?name ?birth ?birthplace ?person ?occupation  WHERE {
     ?person dbpedia-owl:birthPlace ?birthplace.
     ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth .
     ?person foaf:name ?name .
     ?person dbo:occupation :Engineer . 
FILTER (?birth > "1950-01-01"^^xsd:date) .
}
ORDER BY ?name
limit 100

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

SELECT ?person ?name ?birth ?label ?status WHERE {
   ?person dbpedia-owl:nationality ?nationality.
   ?nationality rdfs:label ?label.
   ?person dbo:birthDate ?birth .
   ?person foaf:name ?name .
   ?person dbo:occupation :Engineer .
   ?person dbpedia-owl:status ?status.
FILTER (?birth > "1959-01-01"^^xsd:date) 
FILTER (lang(?label) = "en") 
}
ORDER BY ?name
